dṛṣṭicittaparikhedaparityāgāya kadācit karhicit diśo vyavalokayet. atha kadācit kaścit tatsamīpam āgacchet, tadā tasya praticchāyāmātraṃ viditvā svāgatavādena saṃtoṣaṇārthaṃ vilokayet. anyathā tatra tasyāvadhyānenākuśalaṃ prasavet.

<commentary>mārge 'pi tathādṛṣṭer gacchata upaghātaparihārārtham āha.

bhayahetucaurādipratipattyarthaṃ caturdiśam iti krameṇa. anyathātmabhāvasya rakṣā kṛtā na syāt. sarvadigvyavalokanaṃ tu kriyamāṇam auddhatyopaghātaparihārārthaṃ sthitvā kartavyam. pṛṣṭhato vyavalokanaṃ parāvṛtya paścān mukhībhūya.</commentary>

asamādhānasya ca rakṣaṇām āha. saret puraḥ apasaret paścāt. prapātādyupaghātaṃ nirīkṣya ca. evam ity uktakramadiśā svaparahitaprayojanam avagamya pratipattisāro bhavet.